OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,FNottingham Forest hold a slender
OL,8,Fadvantage over Aston Villa and took a
OL,9,Fgiant step towards their first major
OL,10,FEuropean final in 46 years, after a 1-
OL,11,F0 win in the first leg of their Europa
OL,12,FLeague semi-final tie.
OL,14,FIt was a night of defensive heroics,
OL,15,Fclinical finishing and a VAR
OL,16,Fcontroversy that left Unai Emery
OL,17,Funcharacteristically fuming.
OL,19,FWhile Villa controlled the early
OL,20,Ftempo, it was Forest who carved out
OL,21,Fthe game's best opportunities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,FThe deadlock nearly broke early on,
OL,8,Fonly for World Cup winner Emiliano
OL,9,FMartinez to produce what many are
OL,10,Fcalling the save of the season.
OL,12,FThe Villa skipper looked stunned
OL,13,Fhimself as he clawed the ball off the
OL,14,Fgoal line, reproducing a similar save
OL,15,Fto what won him save of the season at
OL,16,Fthe City Ground last season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,FForest's own number one Stefan Ortega
OL,8,Fproved equally immovable. Heading into
OL,9,Fthe second half, he denied Ollie
OL,10,FWatkins from close range, arguably
OL,11,FVilla's best opening of the night.
OL,13,FMeet the family with divided loyalties
OL,14,Fahead of Forest v Villa in Europe -
OL,15,Fthe Reeve family home is decorated
OL,16,Fwith Forest and Villa memorabilia -
OL,17,Fand they'll be split down the middle.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,FThe decisive moment though came in the
OL,8,F71st minute. After a lengthy VAR check
OL,9,Ffor handball, Chris Wood stepped up
OL,10,Ffrom the penalty spot to slot home his
OL,11,Ffirst Europa League goal since October.
OL,13,FBut the game will be remembered for
OL,14,Fanother VAR controversy.
OL,16,FUnai Emery, demanding respect for the
OL,17,Freferee on the pitch, was critical of
OL,18,Fthe lack of VAR intervention for an
OL,19,Fearlier challenge on Ollie Watkins
OL,20,Ffrom his fellow England international
OL,21,FElliot Anderson.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,FKnown often for his composure in
OL,8,Finterviews and post-match, the game
OL,9,Fhad clearly made a very unhappy Unai.
OL,11,F"It's a huge mistake, huge mistake!
OL,12,FBecause Ollie Watkins was close to
OL,13,Fbreak his ankle. And the VAR - its his
OL,14,Fresponsibility. I don't understand
OL,15,Fwhy. He must give us an explanation
OL,16,Fabout it. Because it's crazy!"
OL,18,FDespite a tumultuous season and
OL,19,Fgrowing injury list, Forest boss Vitor
OL,20,FPereira lauded his side's resilience.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,F"The spirit of this team, even when we
OL,8,Fchange the players. Even with
OL,9,Finjuries. Everyone is ready to compete
OL,10,Fand help the team in this moment. This
OL,11,Fmakes me proud. You look to the bench
OL,12,Fand you feel they want to go inside
OL,13,Fand help the team.
OL,15,FHis goalkeeper Ortega echoed his
OL,16,Fmanager's sentiment and mentality
OL,17,Fshift.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,F"The manager said to us a couple of
OL,8,Fweeks ago that we can turn the bad
OL,9,Fseason how it started into a good one.
OL,10,FIt seems everyone seems to be ready -
OL,11,Fit doesn't matter who's playing".
OL,13,F"We can go for it now".
OL,15,FDespite the loss though, in the Villa
OL,16,Fcamp is a mood of quiet defiance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,FKonsa, who was arguably Villa's best
OL,8,Fplayer last night, remained confident
OL,9,Fthat the tie is far from over and that
OL,10,Fthe Villa faithful should keep the
OL,11,Fbelief.
OL,13,F"We're a confident bunch of boys. We
OL,14,Fknow how good we are at home. And I'm
OL,15,Fsure if we believe, next week will be
OL,16,Ffine".
OL,18,FAs the tie shifts to Villa Park, the
OL,19,Fstatistics offer a fascinating tug of
OL,20,Fwar for both sets of fans:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777669904
OL,3,CVAR controversy, VAR penalty and VAR
OL,4,Cgoal - VAR is the headline at City
OL,5,CGround
OL,7,FWith a 1-0 aggregate lead Forest
OL,8,Ftravel to Villa knowing that avoiding
OL,9,Fdefeat would be enough to see them
OL,10,Fthrough to the final in Istanbul.
OL,12,FBut for Villa, a nine-game European
OL,13,Fwinning streak may have ended, but
OL,14,Ftheir status as favourites on home
OL,15,Fsoil surely remains intact.
OL,17,FFor two clubs with immense European
OL,18,Fpedigree, the stakes aren't just about
OL,19,Fa trophy - it's about giving a whole
OL,20,Fnew generation of fans something to
OL,21,Fdream about.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
